nadir (0.3-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Key mode bug fixed when context menu is shown.
    XGrabKey replaced by XQueryKeyMap.
    Code taken from xspy (Jon A. Maxwell <jmaxwell@acm.vt.edu>)
  * KEYCODE set to F7 code 
  * Nadir is now able to work along with a virtual keyboard

